The application mainframe will displayed in two parts the left part,
will have the search bar. If they click search the map will zoom to the current point or 
if they click it will show text explaining driving instructions. 
Then the right side will have the actual map. In the map on the top left there will 
be a slider that will determine zoom level. Then when a user just clicks on a point 
the node selected will be highlighted and the address will be put into the search bar
and the user can then click driving instructions to get driving directions. 
In addition to pan the user can just click and drag.